rows.label: tlk42300081_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Someone steal top-secret spec
document holding details of new
board game that Seesee was writing!

rows.label: tlk42300081_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Seesee was so looking forward to
people of Luxuria sharing fun for all
family, ages 3+!

rows.label: tlk42300081_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh-meeeeh?! Friends will
get spec document back for Seesee?!
Seesee never heard such kind words!

rows.label: tlk42300081_04_msg0005
rows.name:
OK! Seesee will count on friends to get
document back!

rows.label: tlk42300081_04_msg0006
rows.name:
If possible, would like friends to
retrieve before info gets sold on
black market!
